1. Create a cookbook using which we can create user, while invoking that cookbook we can pass user name
2. Modify above cookbook to delete user
3. Create a cookbook to setup a system, it may involve
  a.) Installing required softwares
  b.) Checking out latest code
  c.) Setting up timezone of system
  d.) Other things that you can think of i.e migrating a software from one version to another one
The idea behind above cookbook is to streamline new people on-boarding purpose or to enable quick transition to another project
